name: Protos
tagline: Protos is an aftermarket firmware based on CyanogenMod. Now it is open-source
body:
![Protos Logo](http://protos.eu.tf/img/main.png)
# **Welcome to the Protos Github page**

**Protos** is an aftermarekt firmware based on CyanogenMod for devices running
Android.
For more information, check [protos-rom.tk](http://protos.eu.tf)

This page won't be updated anymore. See the [official page of Protos](http://protos.eu.tf)


The team:
* FD1999 - Main developer and idea; scripts; base ROM
* paul.n - Server, Logo, Bootanimation, help
* marcomarinho9 - Protos 9 for LG-P500

Quick links:

* [Official page](http://protos.eu.tf)
* [Protos Forum](http://protos-forum.eu.tf)
* [Protos Blog](http://protosrom.wordpress.com)
